::Koj::

Koj on top of Inu-Yasha takeing the Tetsusaiga from its holder on 
Inu-Yasha's side looking at the rusty katana "Inu-Yasha circle wide and drop 
me off behind the Enemy you get the others out."

::Inu-Yasha::

Looks at Koj and growls low to show his dislike of the plan.

::Koj::

Koj looks at Inu-Yasha "I'm counting on you?" Koj jumps off Inu-Yasha 
landing in a tree a few meters behind the Alliance starts to focus on the 
change and enters chameleon mode blending in with the surrounding swamp.


::Inu-Yasha::

Inu-Yasha flies low crashing through trees landing near Tavatorn and Dinobot 
shields them with his Wings. Inu-Yasha signals for the 2 maximals to get on 
his back.

::Koj::

Koj standing in a tree a few feet behind Dark One. Koj slowly spilts his 
hand and whips it forward sending a long Metallic Chain out trying to wrap 
around the back of Dark Ones Neck.
